title: iPhone 15 Pro Max durability test ends with big surprise
description: Zack Nelson's smartphone durability tests are legendary. And this one on the new iPhone 15 Pro Max ends in an unexpected way.

title: Watch NASA’s capsule with asteroid samples hurtling to Earth
description: Watch the key moments from NASA's first-ever sample return mission, from spotting the capsule streaking across the sky to its arrival in a clean room.

title: Chocolate mousse in space is more important than you think
description: An astronaut aboard the ISS has just used a purpose-built machine to make chocolate mousse, a creation that could prove vital for future space voyages.
